title: G-Shock Aviation featuring the GA1000-1A Mens Watch Collecti
description: Introducing the Twin Sensor GA1000 Men's Watch Collection. Offering digital compass with a single press as well a built in thermometer. The GA1000 also has a Neon Illuminator that offers an ultra violet effect to the dial and face. All G-Shock Aviation watches are not complete unless they are Shock Resistant, 200M Water resistant... Not to mention the GA1000 has World Time capability for 48 city + UTC and a 1/100th chronograph.
